## Talk about US, security, and tech
- Mentioned European boycott of Microsoft, Apple
- Concern over US tech as possible security threat
- Trump called major global national security threat

## Food, diet, and eating
- Someone at about 1,000 calories today
- Discussion of eating Kiev with fingers
- Greek yogurt with pesto suggested as easy sauce

## Home, flooring, and games
- Looking at flooring style, debating copying exactly
- Comment that identical flooring feels like cheating, copying
- Mention of game with specific floor style repeated everywhere

## Kids, screens, and TV
- Child watching game videos on tablet
- Decision for mom to watch TV in lounge
- Others encouraged to leave child with tablet and go

## Tech use and switching off
- Suggestion to use phones for better quality recording
- Concern that headphones stop others accessing person
- Intention expressed to ‚Äúturn off for the night‚Äù

## Next steps
- Relax, enjoy tea, and have some quiet time
- Use yogurt-pesto mix as quick future sauce
